t: Deep Dive into Amazon's Category Benchmark Report
s: March 13, 2023 - While there is a lot left to interpretation, we've done our best to explain what the report contains and more importantly, how you can use this data. Ready? Here we go... t: Amazon Sponsored Brands Category Benchmark Report
s: It tells you how many impressions represent the median (50%), how many represent the bottom 25%, and how many represent the top 25%. That way, if a brand sees that its impressions are below the median number given by Amazon, it knows that its performance is less than extraordinary.
